      Pierce Polkiss was a very ordinary man. How ordinary a person can be a simple shopkeeper on the territory of "Empire 88". He praised the gods for the fact that the Kaiser and his henchmen did not dig up his story further than his parents, and therefore he could easily be a carrier of the fourth part of the Jewish blood, while keeping his small but quite profitable business in one of the gang territories. Of course, part of the income he had to give up "Empire", but it was the lesser evil of two possible.
      On its territory the gang tried to maintain order and legality, Polkiss even witnessed a few skirmishes stray bandits and night patrols "Empire". Ended which is not in favor of the guest performers. This, however, did not stop petty crime like stealing, however, the destruction of such was tantamount to completely get rid of cockroaches is to get rid of you can, but sooner or later they will come back.
      But in this moment time he was would glad, if would the Imperials worked out with street punks, which, proud of its "communication with "Empire", that in common people meant "potential cannon fodder", has behaved absolutely is unseemly.
      Rules, of course, they knew nothing, except threats and theft, never did, but it was still vybeshivaet Polkiss to the core.
      Today these nerds cornered again. A group of shaven-headed young men with tattoos of varying degrees of nationalism fell into his shop with the appearance of kings inspecting the plebs. And all would be nothing if these gentlemen insolent, straight from under his nose would not have pulled almost a box of beer.
      There was nothing he could do. The police reacted very inertly to calls from "gangster" areas, plus to all any special proofs Mr. Polkiss couldn't provide because the small shop wasn't equipped with security cameras.
      Now, as he scrolled through the events of the day in his head and dangled the tape of the electronics store, Mr. Polkiss Felt a sudden surge of determination. In the end, the police and the "Empire" will not be able to respond if he will be able to provide the theft?
      With these thoughts, Mr. Polkiss Pressed the "add to cart" button, and the brand new security camera with good color correction and a night filter began its journey from the warehouse to its new owner…

      
